room_title: Escape room "The Orphan" by Breakout CoMo in Columbia (MO)
room_description: It was just another day at the Boone County Orphanage, until a young girl showed up out of thin air. With her she brought mysteries and secrets that haunted the orphanage. Many tried to get answers, but they were unsuccessful. It’s up to you to find out who she was…and where she went.
